<p>Ridgeback is a midsize indoor robot platform that uses an omni-drive to move manipulators and heavy payloads with ease.
The omnidirectional base provides precision positioning in constrained environments and comes fully integrated with onboard computer, front and optional rear laser scanners and an IMU.
Ridgeback offers native ROS and Gazebo integration and is plug-and-play compatible with Clearpathâ€™s wide range of robot accessories.</p>
